oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Capitol Towers Apartments Nearing Completion, 1960
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of Capitol Towers Apartments nearing completion, 1 November 1960. The apartments were located at 510 Gay Street, within the Capitol Hill Redevelopment Project area (Parcel "E"). Photographed by the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
